      <td>${e.tierReason}</td>
    </tr>`).join('')}
  </table>
</div>
` : ''}

${tiers[1].length > 0 ? `
<div class="section">
  <div class="section-title p1">🟡 P1 — 本周跟进 (${tiers[1].length}人)</div>
